291
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:08,260
True.

292
00:15:09,620 --> 00:15:10,460
We've almost

293
00:15:10,540 --> 00:15:11,740
cleared our stock.

294
00:15:11,980 --> 00:15:13,380
After taking over LYS,

295
00:15:13,740 --> 00:15:15,300
shouldn't we also

296
00:15:15,300 --> 00:15:16,196
