376
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,860
Captain Su is taking the lead today.

377
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:53,300
He'll treat us once we're done.

378
00:18:53,420 --> 00:18:54,100
Great.

379
00:19:05,900 --> 00:19:07,020
