393
00:20:20,940 --> 00:20:21,700
Looks fine.

394
00:20:23,180 --> 00:20:23,860
Take this.

395
00:20:25,940 --> 00:20:27,020
I can tolerate anything

396
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:28,180
