836
00:40:51,300 --> 00:40:53,700
Feet parallel, shoulder-width apart.

837
00:40:53,820 --> 00:40:55,300
Grab the wrist with your right hand.

838
00:40:55,420 --> 00:40:57,620
Step forward and lift the back

839
